---
const tags = ["Python", "Lua", "TypeScript", "Linux", "Automation"];
---

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="about__inner">
    <div class="about__text">
      <p class="about__greeting">
        <span data-pl>Cześć, jestem</span>
        <span data-en>Hi, I'm</span>
      </p>
      <h1 class="about__name">Daniel Pardej</h1>
      <h2 class="about__role">Heryod</h2>

      <p class="about__bio" data-pl>
        Pasjonat nowych technologii z Łodzi. Doświadczenie buduję poprzez
        autorskie projekty - od zarządzania i technicznego utrzymania serwera
        FiveM, po własny system automatyzacji domowej oparty na Home
        Assistancie. Obecnie intensywnie rozwijam się w obszarze AI/ML oraz
        rozpoczynam zaoczne studia na kierunku Informatyka, szukając pierwszych
        wyzwań zawodowych.
      </p>
      <p class="about__bio" data-en>
        Tech enthusiast from Łódź. I build my experience through hands-on
        personal projects, ranging from managing and maintaining a FiveM server
        to designing a custom Home Assistant automation ecosystem. Currently, I
        am expanding my skills in AI/ML and pursuing a part-time Bachelor's
        degree in Computer Science, ready to transition into my first
        professional role.
      </p>

      <div class="about__tags">
        {tags.map((s) => <span class="tag">{s}</span>)}
      </div>

      <div class="about__cta">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/heryod"
          class="btn btn--primary"
          target="_blank"
        >
          GitHub
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:kontakt@heryod.works" class="btn btn--ghost">
          <span data-pl>Kontakt</span>
          <span data-en>Contact</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!--
    <div class="about__avatar">
      <img src="/images/heryod.webp" alt="heryod" width="350" height="350" />
    </div> -->
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg-card) 42%, transparent);
    display: flex;
  }

  .about__inner {
    min-width: 0;
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .about__text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .about__greeting {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .about__name {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.35rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .about__role {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .about__bio {
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 46rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about__tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .tag {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--accent);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .about__cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn--primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
  }
  .btn--primary:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .btn--ghost {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .btn--ghost:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .about__avatar img {
    width: clamp(250px, 25vw, 350px);
    height: clamp(250px, 25vw, 350px);
    border-radius: 15%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    filter: grayscale(20%);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about__inner {
      text-align: left;
    }

    .about__tags,
    .about__cta {
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }

    .about__bio {
      margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
